What you need to know:  The World Athletics Championships are programmed from July 15 to 24 in Eugene, Oregon, United States of America while the Commonwealth Games are scheduled for July 28 to August 8 in Birmingham, England.AK President Jack Tuwei said that the World marathon women's defending champion Ruth Chepng'etich and two-time World Half Marathon champion Geoffrey Kamworor will lead team for the World Athletics Championships.